Tell me about the "plan" you
were all talking about.

rows.label: qst650105_msg0003
rows.name: And what will you do... if you know...?

rows.label: qst650105_msg0008
rows.name:
will gather at the descent to the
Chansagh Wastes in the Old Industrial
District of the Superbian Empire.

rows.label: qst650105_msg0009

avenge Marveni-sama's death...!

Our preparations will soon be
complete... It saves us the

rows.name:
Well, well... It seems we have
no choice but to settle this.

rows.label: qst650105_msg0018
rows.name: But, T-elos Re:, don't overdo it.
